Name: Blade Walker
About the game: Why do you dream of electric sheep? Will you solve your life's problems and escape from the city? Or will your dreams consume you? The answers likely lie outside your room, so first you need to unlock the door. Find clues and solve puzzles to advance through rooms until all of your problems are solved. Left mouse or E to interact
